data.description: Here is your chance at Waterfront Living with a beautiful view overlooking Tainter lake. Close proximity to renowned local restaurants and access to the water and fishing right out your back door and off of the roll in dock. Oversized 1 car garage could be converted into additional gathering space for those coming to enjoy the lake and the awesome fire pit in the back yard or store the toys for the water in the off-season.
